column5: Here is a last ditch effort anyone got any contacts at Yuk Yuks in Toronto. I really want to buy tickets to the Norm Mac Donald show there tonight but it's sold out. I thought one of you may have a guy that know a guy that could hook me up!  Dave Mercer
Dave just grab a mic and look in the mirror. You are way better than Norm anyway!
The Mrs wants to be a part of your act, next year, Dave
